For Users Table:

CREATE TABLE Users ( 
	user_ID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,  
	username VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, 
	password VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, 
	admin_priveliges BIT(1) NOT NULL,
	real_name VARCHAR(128),
	email VARCHAR(128),
	phone VARCHAR(128),
	upload_permission BIT(1) NOT NULL
);

---------------------------------------------------

For Trips Table:

CREATE TABLE Trips ( 
	trip_ID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY, 
	user_ID INT NOT NULL, 
	source VARCHAR(256), 
	destination VARCHAR(256), 
	trip_date_range VARCHAR(256), 
	timestamp_uploaded TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	additional_information VARCHAR(256)
);

---------------------------------------------------

Template for a trip table: Note that a new table will be created for each trip in the Trips table.  
The name of each new table will be the cooresponding trip_ID from the Trips table.

CREATE TABLE <trip_ID> ( 
	data_ID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,  
	timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, 
	GPS_location VARCHAR(256), 
	humidity FLOAT,
	temperature FLOAT,
	impact INT,
	atmospheric_pressure FLOAT,
	orientation VARCHAR(256)
);

